There was a nod from BUMP as NIGHTLIGHT made her choice. "Good
animals, both of them." BUMP's voice was somewhat distracted as he was
also working on getting NIGHTSHIFT to his recharging chamber. Finally
with a heave he lifted the Maximal into the air and began to walk him
over to a cubical.

BUMP looked NIGHTLIGHT and ELITA a small perfunctory smile on his
face, "Okay, I will see what I can do for you in just a moment. We
should have scans of animals in the data bank."

As BUMP set NIGHTSHIFT into his repair chamber he turned back to
NIGHTLIGHT, "Does that mean you will fall under Torca's command? He is
the leader of the Fuzors?"

(TAG)

Preston
